                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Done managing tenants or maintaining a vacant property? We'll take the burden off your hands 
                        with a straightforward cash purchase—no more late-night calls or repair bills.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
