                        Moving to a smaller space? We make the transition smooth.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-slate-100">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Fire or Water Damage</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                        Buy damaged properties as-is, no restoration required.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-slate-100">
